About This Company
Founded in 1992, Spadamco Holdings Limited is a privately owned, regional holding company, with interests across a wide range of industries. From the start, our goal has been the constant pursuit of excellence, in everything that we do. Spadamco’s strong association with luxury is well deserved, as we have continued to bring world-class F&B; and retail brands, such as La Cure Gourmande, The Caviar House and Prunier and Osh Kosh B’Gosh to the GCC region. Within the engineering world, our organization, Applied Corrosion Technology, has grown into a regional leader in anti-corrosion services. Despite all of this, the quest for excellence is still at the core of everything we do at Spadamco, and our experienced management team is constantly seeking new and innovative ways to improve our products and services. ®
